  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (Landed house projects) [Ang Mo Kio | 5/6 days | up to $3500] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Quantity Surveyor (Landed house projects)</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Salary: $3000 -$3500</strong></p>\n<p><strong>5/6 days, 9.30am-6.30pm; Saturday depends on workload or by appointment</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Address: Ang Mo Kio</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare, negotiate and analyse costs for tenders and contracts for private landed projects.</li>\n  <li>Handle all contractual matters in relation to cost and time with the clients, Architects, Engineers, Designers, Project coordinators and subcontractors.</li>\n  <li>Valuing completed work and prepare claim settlement and notification correspondences to clients.</li>\n  <li>Monitor projects including materials and subcontractor cost forecast are strictly adhered to the agreed budget.</li>\n  <li>Call for supplier / subcontractor quotation and compare with tender details.</li>\n  <li>Able to do Quotation/Bill of quantity with Just Architects drawing.</li>\n  <li>Able to fill in the tender document.</li>\n  <li>Other quantity surveying related duties for building projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Quantity Surveying , and with 2 years of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Experience in landed house projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
